OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,FBut it is not an endorsable offence,
OL,7,Fmeaning drivers are currently only
OL,8,Flikely to face a fine rather than
OL,9,Fpoints or a ban.
OL,11,FAt the Thatcham Research facility near
OL,12,FNewbury, engineers are continuously
OL,13,Ftesting car safety features, including
OL,14,Fthe effectiveness of the seatbelt.
OL,16,FThe exercises involve crashing a
OL,17,Fvehicle, with a dummy inside wearing a
OL,18,Fseat belt, but both passengers are not
OL,19,Fwearing seat belts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
