CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,FPrincipal engineer for automotive
OL,7,Fsafety, Alex Thompson said: "Seat
OL,8,Fbelts are hugely important in terms of
OL,9,Fvehicle safety, that they keep you in
OL,10,Fyour seating position to start with.
OL,12,F"They restrain you in a crash, around
OL,13,Fyour pelvis and around the other
OL,14,Fstrong parts of your body, like your
OL,15,Fshoulder, and they're really designed
OL,16,Fto work with things like airbags to
OL,17,Fstop you from hitting the hard parts
OL,18,Finside of the car."
OL,20,FIn the UK, it is a legal requirement
OL,21,Fto wear a seat belt if one is fitted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,FThe responsibility for wearing a seat
OL,7,Fbelt differs.
OL,9,FDrivers are responsible for ensuring
OL,10,Fchildren under 14 are properly
OL,11,Frestrained, while passengers aged 14
OL,12,Fand over are responsible for wearing
OL,13,Ftheir own seat belts
OL,15,F"If you're caught not wearing a
OL,16,Fseatbelt, you're only subject to to a
OL,17,Frelatively small fine, of about #100,"
OL,18,FMr Thompson added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
