OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,F"That can go up, but there is no
OL,7,Fsanction for you in terms of penalty
OL,8,Fpoints and the, the the government
OL,9,Fsafety strategy is looking at
OL,10,Fincreasing that to make it an offence
OL,11,Fthat that covers that puts penalty
OL,12,Fpoints on your license but not wearing
OL,13,Fa seatbelt."
OL,15,FPolice do stop vehicles if they
OL,16,Fsuspect people aren't wearing a
OL,17,Fseatbelt and some forces are now using
OL,18,FAI cameras to help spot offenders
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
