OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,FSussex Police say all too often they
OL,7,Ffind fatal crashes have a common
OL,8,Ffactor, in occupants failing to wear
OL,9,Fseatbelts.
OL,11,FInspector Vicki Rees from the force
OL,12,Fsaid when people spot officers on
OL,13,Fpatrol they quickly put their
OL,14,Fseatbelts on.
OL,16,F"It tells me that they know they
OL,17,Fshouldn't be doing it but you know
OL,18,Fthey're doing it anyway which is
OL,19,Fdisappointing," she said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,F"If you've not been involved in a
OL,7,Fcrash, it can be really difficult for
OL,8,Fpeople to imagine the forces involved
OL,9,Fand to think you know I've got an
OL,10,Fairbag, I'm driving quite slowly, it
OL,11,Fwon't be a problem.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately in my career and my
OL,14,Fcolleagues will tell you the same,
OL,15,Fwe've seen people involved in crashes
OL,16,Feven at relatively low speeds where
OL,17,Fthey've been thrown out of the front
OL,18,Fof the car, they've been crushed
OL,19,Funderneath cars, they've even gone out
OL,20,Fthe back windscreen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774368667
OL,3,CWhy UK drivers could face tougher
OL,4,Cpenalties for not wearing a seat belt
OL,6,F"It's really really important and a
OL,7,Freally simple thing to do that you
OL,8,Fsecure yourself in the car and that
OL,9,Fyou make sure you do the same with any
OL,10,Fof your passengers, especially
OL,11,Fvulnerable people, you know children
OL,12,Fas well.
OL,14,FThe government consultation on
OL,15,Fseatbelt law is part of their road
OL,16,Fsafety strategy, which aims to reduce
OL,17,Fthe number of road deaths by two
OL,18,Fthirds by 2035.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
